Zortrax 3D Printers

Zortrax is a Polish manufacturer of 3D printers and filaments for the SMB market and rapid prototyping for industries, including robotics and automation, architecture, industrial design, engineering, aviation, industrial automation.

Zortrax is one of the biggest brands in 3D printing, their product line is popular among professionals and industry experts.

The multi award winning Zortrax products are held in high regard for reliability and production quality.

    Zortrax in Australia

    We have been selling Zortrax 3D printers to the engineering and industrial design, education, arts, architecture sectors right across Australia.

    It’s no surprise that Zortrax is one of our more popular 3D printers, the key contributing factors being simplicity, reliability, price and accuracy.

    We carry a wide range of spare parts, the full range of Zortrax materials and offer training, servicing and repairs.
